properties.Name: FocusGroupCustomer
properties.Description:
The one of more Focus Groups that the Customer is a member of.

A special interest group that focuses upon a specific Product or Product usage.

Focus Groups are most often manufacturer-sponsored groups designed to provide feedback directly to the manufacturer regarding their products prior to product mass marketing.

Columns.Name: FocusGroupId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Focus Group.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date of the Focus Group - Customer association.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date of the Focus Group - Customer association.

Columns.Name: FocusGroupMembershipNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional detail regarding the Focus Group membership.
